reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Hard to use
reviews.reviewText: These building blocks are pretty and good for building muscles in little hands but won't stay together and are much smaller than the pictures.. At first the kids loved them but couldn't get any of the pieces to stay together in order to build something. They gave up and didn't go back to them. The carrying container came without the handle. I will be returning this item for something more user friendly. The description also needs to tell you the measurements of the building pieces not the size of the container that holds them.
